text: Ivan Semyonov (born 25 January 1936) is a Soviet equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Soviet male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Soviet Union Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
